 any case in which the Type-I migration of the inner embryo is\nprevented by some mechanism, and not solely to the planet trap scenario.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Nov 2007 06:10:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
